  Reasoning blocks
  Choose whether reasoning is shown inline in the chat.

  1. Off                Keep reasoning out of the main chat.
› 2. Summary (current)  Show reasoning summaries inline while a turn is
                        running.
  3. Raw                Show raw reasoning inline when the provider exposes
                        it.

